## Resin Injection Model


::: {.columns}

::: {.column width="50%"}

::: callout-note

## Forward Problem: 

Find $(\blue{p,\Upsilon})$ given  $\red{u}=\red{(K,\phi)}$.

Darcy flow:
$$
- \nabla \cdot \Big[ \frac{ \red{K(x)}}{\mu} \nabla \blue{p(x,t)} \Big] = 0,\quad \textrm{in}~ \Omega(t) \nonumber
$$

Moving front: $x\in \Upsilon(t)$:

$$
\frac{d \blue{\Upsilon(t)}}{dt}=  -  \frac{\red{K(x)}}{\red{\phi(x)} \mu} \nabla \blue{p(x,t)} \cdot \mathbf{n}(x,t) \nonumber
$$
